<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>⚡ ZOO AI Agent Starter Kit — 48-Hour Flash Deal | 60% OFF</title>
<meta name="description" content="Get the complete AI Agent Starter Kit for just $19 (was $49). Production-ready templates, observability, security scanning — everything to ship your AI agent in 48 hours.">
